{"tid":751714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西甲會長：C朗貪意大利稅率低","createTime":"2018-07-22T06:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T07:56:28.000Z","uid":20634,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4dea534eee66cc3bbde501f8168b21c07de86d","tid":751714,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/1/271/22227631271/22232446775_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F1%2F271%2F22227631271%2F22232446775_600x399.jpg&h=0b958753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基斯坦奴朗拿度以尋找新挑戰為由改投意甲懷抱，不過西甲聯會會長就指C朗此舉無非一個「錢」字作怪。<br />\n<br />\n「C朗投身意甲的決定跟稅率有莫大關係。在西班牙因為『碧咸法案』他要拿收入50%去交稅，在意大利他只要交10萬歐元。換著是你又會怎樣做呢？C朗今次轉會祖記純粹出於經濟理由。」西甲聯會會長泰巴斯（Javier Tebas）對《阿斯報》說。<br />\n<br />\n江湖傳聞當年西班牙為了利誘萬人迷碧咸加盟皇家馬德里，於2004年推出稅務優惠，外籍僱員頭6年稅率低至24%，俗稱「碧咸法案」，但由於財赤當局已於2010年修例，外援球員至少要拿50%收入去交稅，亦引致美斯、C朗等多名球星被指逃稅；那邊廂意大利近年卻修改稅例，讓C朗這類外援每年只需繳交10萬歐元的稅項。"},{"pid":"d50e4395bb254e1edba229024e6575353ba81b28","tid":751714,"uid":163207,"like":16,"dislike":24,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"畀美斯撚到敗走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e06318b4d8eb00339590a69b3110f9091518104","tid":751714,"uid":52265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:38:36.000Z","msg":"政治莫財仲好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bf6a760da2b2ebe6a8b814f630bdf3cf0fd931","tid":751714,"uid":12736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"年年比西班牙追税係人都走啦"},{"pid":"d6d3612799c318de975fae702034622bb62452ec","tid":751714,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"@王騎"},{"pid":"f8bf1b161d44a82c53f60762b09bc13cc303ea6d","tid":751714,"uid":155902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco